data.text:
2024

Competed in long jump, triple jump, 4x100, and 4x400 for 9 meets this season… Competed at SCIAC Championships placing 7th in the 4x100 (45.62), 8th in triple jump with a personal best of 13.02m, and 19th in long jump (19 '3.25). Top career performances this season were 6.16m in long jump and 13.02m in triple jump.

2023 (Track & Field)

Competed in long jump and triple jump events in 8 meets this season… At the SCIAC Championships, placed 11th in the triple jump (12.19m), and set a career best and placed 14th in the long jump (5.84m).... Best finish was 5th in triple jump in the SCIAC Multi-Dual 2 meet.

Mt. Camel High School ‘22

Competed in football, basketball, and track and field in the Palomar league… Tri-sport athlete, First Team All-League in football, triple jump CIF championship, triple jump league champion, First Team All-League/CIF in track, and led the league in sacks in football… Team accomplishments are CIF in Football, basketball and track and field and Palomar league champions.
